label: Unmanaged wood investment before year start
definition: Investment in unmanaged wood technology before year start.

label: Unmanaged wood investment
definition: Investment in unmanaged wood over the years.

label: Managed wood data
definition: Different data and result computed about managed wood.

label: Unmanaged wood data
definition: Different data and result computed about unmanaged wood.

label: Biomass Dry detailed data
definition: Different data about biomass dry production and price.

label: Biomass dry data
definition: Important data about biomass dry that are used by other models.

label: Transport cost
definition: Cost of transport of material in $ per tons.

label: Margin
definition: Factor applied to the total price to take into account commercial margin.

label: Agriculture techno list
definition: List of technologies of agriculture that lost capital.

label: Techno Capital
definition: Capital of the considered technology over the year.

label: Non use capital
definition: Non use capital of the considered technology.

label: Non use capital constraint limit
definition: Non use capital contraint limit. Used for optimization

label: Non use capital constraint reference
definition: Non use capital contraint reference. Used for optimization

label: Max capital utilisation ratio
definition: Maximum rate of utilisation of capital

label: Production df
definition: Output and output net of damage over the years.

label: Growth rate df
definition: Output net of damage growth rate over the years.

label: Detailed Capital df
definition: Capital, usable capital, energy efficiency and E_max over the years.

label: Capital df
definition: Capital and usable capital per year.

label: Productivity df
definition: Productivity and productivity growth rate over years.

label: Sector investment df
definition: Investment in sector per year.

label: Historical output
definition: Dataframe with historical data for output in T$ used for fitting of production functions

label: Historical capital
definition: Dataframe with historical data for capital in T$ used for fitting of production functions

label: Other Land Use and Change Co2 emissions
definition: Value of the CO2 emissions of land use and change. This does not include deforestation and forest sequestration, emission from crop and food development

label: Data for earlier energy efficiency
definition: Dataframe to add extra data and years for energy efficiency fitting. Capital in T$ and energy in Pwh.

label: Weights dataframe
definition: Dataframe with weights by year for fitting.

label: Production function fitting
definition: Input to be activated if we fit the production function. When activated it adds outputs necessary for the fitting.

label: vegetables and fruit calories per day
definition: number of calories coming from vegetables and fruits consumed per day per person.

label: White meat calories per day
definition: number of calories coming from white meat consumed per day per person.

label: Workforce share per sector
definition: Distribution of workforce per economic sector in %. One column per sector. Total of column should be 100.

label: Sectors list
definition: List of sectors

label: Sub-sectors list
definition: List of sub-sectors

label: GDP percentage per section
definition: Percentage of the GDP for each sub-sector

label: GDP per section
definition: GDP values of sub-sectors in a sector

label: GDP per section
definition: GDP values of sub-sectors in all sectors

label: Energy consumption percentage per section
definition: Percentage of the energy consumption for each sub-sector

label: Energy consumption per section
definition: Energy consumption per section

label: Energy carbon intensity
definition: Total CO2 equivalent emitted by energy mix divided by total energy production of energy mix

label: Energy emission per section
definition: Energy emission per section

label: Non-energy emission per $GDP per section
definition: Non energy CO2 emission per $GDP per section

label: Non-energy emission per section
definition: Non-energy emission per section

label: Total emission per section
definition: Total emission per section

label: Total emissions
definition: Total emissions (sum of energy emission and non-energy emission)

label: Total emissions detailed
definition: Energy/non-energy/total emissions

label: GDP per group
definition: GDP-PPP adjusted by group

label: GDP share per group
definition: GDP-PPP adjusted share percentage by group

label: GDP per country
definition: GDP-PPP adjusted per country

label: Non energy emissions per section
definition: Non energy emissions per section and per sector dictionary

label: Energy consumption per section
definition: Energy consumption per section and per sector dictionary

label: Energy emissions per section
definition: Energy emissions per section and per sector dictionary

label: Total emissions per section
definition: Total emissions per section and per sector dictionary
